                <li>&nbsp;&nbsp; Dimensional tolerance = +/- 0.032. Angle tolerance = +/- 2째.</li>
                <li>&nbsp;&nbsp; Clear anodized finish.</li>
                <li>&nbsp;&nbsp; Adhesive included.</li>
                <li>&nbsp;&nbsp; For non-standard requirements, provide drawing for pre-approval.</li>
            </ul>
        </span>

        <div style="page-break-after: auto;">
            <table style="border-collapse: collapse; width:100%; border:black; border-style:solid;">
                <tr>
                    <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding:6px;">
                        <b>FOR INPRO USE ONLY</b>
                    </td>
                    <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding:6px;">
                        {!customForm.quoteRecord.Inside_Rep__c}
                    </td>
                    <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding:6px;">
                        Customer Order #:
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding:6px;">
                        Form  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  of        
                    </td>
                    <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding:6px;">
                        Inpro Drawing: N/A
                    </td>
                    <td style="border: 1px solid black;padding:6px;">
                        Inpro #:
                    </td>
                </tr>            
            </table>
            </div>


        </apex:form>
        </body>
        </apex:repeat>
        </html>
        </apex:outputText>


